data.description: Rare opportunity to own a townhome like this in such a highly desirable area!  Open concept main living space with vaulted ceilings and south facing windows providing plenty of natural light.  The main living level has the kitchen, living and dining areas.  It also includes the primary and second bedroom and a full bath.  In winter warm yourself by the gas fireplace, in summer enjoy yourmorning  or evening libations from the covered front deck. The primary bedroom has a large, walk-in closet and adjoining bathroom. Downstairs features one bedroom, laundry, a full bathroom, and the family room that could qualify as a bedroom with minimal work.  Access to the backyard from the house is through the sliding door from the family room.  The two car garage is large and includes built in shelving along one wall and a painted floor.  Buyer to verify all information.
